query:
UPDATE 
                http_trigger 
            SET 
                route_path = $1, 
                route_path_key = $2,
                workspaced_route = $3,
                wrap_body = $4,
                raw_string = $5,
                authentication_resource_path = $6,
                script_path = $7, 
                path = $8, 
                is_flow = $9, 
                http_method = $10, 
                static_asset_config = $11, 
                edited_by = $12, 
                email = $13, 
                is_async = $14, 
                authentication_method = $15, 
                edited_at = now(), 
                is_static_website = $16,
                error_handler_path = $17,
                error_handler_args = $18,
                retry = $19
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $20 AND 
                path = $21
